    "content": "A truss, as shown in the figure, is carrying $$180$$ $$kN$$ load at node $${L_2}.$$ The force in the diagonal member $${M_2}{U_4}$$ will be \n<img class=\"question-image\" src=\"https://imagex.cdn.examgoal.net/pe50I3Zxou72aakS9/SZTQD4hA0SF8ZCJKxROWYiYrq1DYV/b3Z6LfgV9dapRTyVSUWs1F/image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"GATE CE 2003 Structural Analysis - Truss Question 7 English\"> ",
    "options": [
